text:
Ordered crispy pancake with peanut for $1.80.

Don't understand why it is more expensive than original when amount is lesser. Nevertheless it has all i am looking for in Chinese pancake the crispy and the sweet and savory peanut filling. A rare find.

Exceptional find in a neighborhood market. This is the chewy type MJK which is freshly made upon ordering. Highly recommend to eat this while it’s hot for the perfectly crispy “wings”. Generous dollop of the peanut spread which has a crunchy peanut butter consistency. The pancake thickness is just right as well - has a good, soft bouncy bite to it. Craving this again as I am typing out this review!
Great pancakes. The auntie was very patient while doing the crispy pancake. Contrary to some reviews, the auntie was very friendly to me. Perhaps it’s because there was less people.
Strongly recommend!! Especially the mini ones where u can choose many fillings to try!!

Come here for really good peanut pancake. But be prepared to wait and service is definitely not a strength here. The mood can be as gloomy as the thunderstorms in Sgp.  Buy and it fresh, no regrets. Just dun expect Aunty to say thank you or welcome your orders!
